OL,3,CStaff error behind hidden #30 million
OL,4,Chospital projected overspend
OL,6,FAn independent review has concluded
OL,7,Fthat "personnel failings" were to
OL,8,Fblame for the hidden, spiralling
OL,9,Festimated price tag of Guernsey's
OL,10,Fhospital modernisation project.
OL,12,FThe report was commissioned after
OL,13,Fcivil servants were found to be
OL,14,F'withholding key costs' from
OL,15,Fpoliticians - they were subsequently
OL,16,Fsacked.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
