OL,3,CStaff error behind hidden #30 million
OL,4,Chospital projected overspend
OL,6,FThe reviewer said "three key
OL,7,Fpersonnel" were at fault for not
OL,8,Falerting politicians that the plans
OL,9,Fhad gone an estimated #30 million over
OL,10,Fbudget.
OL,12,FThis was however described as an
OL,13,F"error of judgment" rather than any
OL,14,F"wilful attempt to mislead".
OL,16,FIt took 10 months for civil servants
OL,17,Fin the Project Management Team to
OL,18,Fnotify the Health and Social Care
OL,19,FCommittee about the revised figures
OL,20,Fand then another two months for the
OL,21,FChief Minister to find out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
