OL,6,F"Structural flaws" were therefore
OL,7,Ffound not to be "the immediate cause
OL,8,Fof the problem" and the review
OL,9,Fconcluded "the underlying project
OL,10,Fprocess adopted by the States is fit
OL,11,Ffor purpose".
OL,13,FHowever, the report added "that in
OL,14,Frelation to capital projects,
OL,15,Fgenerally there needs to be a cultural
OL,16,Fchange in thinking and decision
OL,17,Fmaking" and a "clearer reporting line".
