OL,6,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FLyndon Trott, told ITV Channel: "I
OL,8,Ftake enormous comfort from the
OL,9,Findependent reviewers conclusion and
OL,10,Ftaxpayers can take comfort from the
OL,11,Ffact that the structures in place are
OL,12,Fadequate and fit for purpose.
OL,14,F"There is no accounting for the
OL,15,Foccasional strange misjudgment."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
