OL,6,FIn a statement he added: "It is
OL,7,Fimportant to remember this relates to
OL,8,Fa potential cost increase but not an
OL,9,Factual overspend and we are still of
OL,10,Fthe view that the project can and
OL,11,Fshould be completed within its
OL,12,Fapproved budget".
OL,14,FHowever, Deputy Carl Meerveld paints a
OL,15,Fmore damning picture.
OL,17,FHe said: "Politicians were left out of
OL,18,Fthe loop completely ... This was a
OL,19,Fsystemic failure within the
OL,20,Forganisation of the Civil Service."
