OL,4,Chospital projected overspend
OL,6,FAn error of judgment, that's how the
OL,7,Fwithheld #30 million projected
OL,8,Foverspend of the Hospital
OL,9,FModernisation Project is being
OL,10,Flabelled.
OL,12,FThere was no cover up and there are no
OL,13,Fstructural flaws to blame for the lack
OL,14,Fof transparency over the bloating
OL,15,Fmulti-million pound project.
OL,17,FThe blame, it seems, lies squarely on
OL,18,Fthe shoulders of three nameless civil
OL,19,Fservants.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
