OL,4,Chospital projected overspend
OL,6,FThese are the findings of States
OL,7,Flawyer Martin Thornton's report, who
OL,8,Fwas commissioned to independently
OL,9,Finvestigate the chain of events that
OL,10,Fled to politicians being misled in
OL,11,Fregards to a project they were meant
OL,12,Fto be overseeing.
OL,14,FBut the President of Health and Social
OL,15,FCare (HSC) hasn't gotten off lightly.
OL,16,FDeputy Al Brouard and his Committee
OL,17,Fwere scalded by Mr Thornton for not
OL,18,Ftelling Policy and Resources (P&R)
OL,19,Fsooner.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
