OL,4,Chospital projected overspend
OL,6,FThe projected overspend was known to
OL,7,FHSC during a notable debate about
OL,8,Ftrying to find funding for the
OL,9,FTransforming Education Programme, a
OL,10,Fheated meeting where finances and
OL,11,Ffunding were a crucial part of the
OL,12,Fdecision making process.
OL,14,FMr Thornton has since said that the
OL,15,FCommittee had a duty to tell P&R
OL,16,Fsooner, as the increased figures were
OL,17,Fpretty well established.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
